      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRIMAL BOOST (3) was a last start winner (25.74) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Form from her last run is proving strong. Well placed and will be tough to beat. GOAL KICKER (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 5.5 lengths fifth (20.51) but recorded best time of the card when winning five back. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. NANGAR MCGRAW (4) struggled for best form latest, finishing 4th (18.90) in a NG at Temora. Has won here at this journey. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Should be about the money. BING BONUS (6) must be included in main hopes on latest effort.",
